# Generated registries and index files (regenerated by `pnpm run generate:toc`).
# Exception: curated phase index files (auto_generated: false in frontmatter,
# e.g. content/tools/{phase}/_index.md from the tools-vertical reorganisation)
# have a hand-authored preamble above an `<!-- AUTO-GENERATED REGISTRY... -->`
# marker and must be tracked; only the registry section below the marker is
# regenerated in place. See scripts/generate-toc.js and
# scripts/rebuild-phase-indexes.js.
content/**/_registry.md
content/**/_index.md
